Language Services, excluding BSL
Trafford Council requires translation and interpretation providers to provide language support to non-English speakers in the provision of:
•	Face to Face interpreting for interviews, meetings, consultation and social care requirements (spoken);
•	Telephone interpreting to facilitate ease of communications (spoken);
•	Document translation services, including Braille, large print, easy Read and Audio Transcription,
•	Video interpreting (i.e. video conference)

